{"article_id":"LTpG2npyWfTsSnqB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The 2016 GOP hopeful","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"most helped by Jeb Bush ' s early stumbles ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"or so the pundit wisdom goes ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"is Florida Sen. Marco Rubio .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"The two men share the same home state ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"both are expected to appeal to Latino voters ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"and Bush was expected to soak up a lot of the Florida money","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that might have buoyed Rubio ' s presidential hopes .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"But lately ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"with Bush looking ever weaker ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"thanks most recently to his awful answers on Iraq ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Rubio was thought to have an argument","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that he ' s a stronger candidate than the nominal front-runner .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Until Sunday , that is .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"That ' s when Rubio joined Bush in the ( latest )","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Iraq war quagmire .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"There ' s got to be some karmic justice in the fact","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"that two leading GOP presidential candidates have humiliated themselves","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"trying to figure out how to handle the war politically .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Confronted by Fox ' s Chris Wallace about his own seeming flip flop on the question","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"of whether ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"if he knew then","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"what we know now ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"he ' d have invaded Iraq ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Rubio tried to deny","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"he ' d given different answers .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Then he challenged Wallace","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"for asking the question .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"At first Rubio tried to insist","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"it ' s unfair to use hindsight","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"to critique President George W. Bush ' s decision .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"\" Based on what we know now ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"I wouldn ' t have thought","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Manny Paquiao was gon na beat...in that fight... \"","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Rubio seemed unable to recall the name of Paquiao ' s opponent , victor Floyd Mayweather .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Or else he realized","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"it was a mistake to compare a war","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"that killed 4,000 American soldiers","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"to a boxing match .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Nah , he probably just forgot the name .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"For a while , he held fast to his assertion","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"that it was not a mistake .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"\" It ' s not a mistake , \"","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"he said repeatedly .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"\" I still say","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"it was not a mistake","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"because the president was presented with intelligence","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"that said","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"Iraq had weapons of mass destruction ,","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"it was governed by a man","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"who had committed atrocities in the past with weapons of mass destruction . \"","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"When Wallace pushed him to say","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"whether he ' d call it a mistake ,","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"even knowing about the faulty intelligence ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"he still seemed to say no :","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"\" The world is a better place","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"because Saddam Hussein is not there... \"","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"he began .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Then he seemed say yes :","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"George Bush would have moved forward on the invasion ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"and he certainly wouldn ' t have gotten Congressional approval . ''","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"Wallace missed the chance","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"to say","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"that George W. Bush did not , in fact , admit","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"the invasion was a mistake","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"once he knew","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"the WMD intelligence was faulty .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"\" There are things","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"we got wrong in Iraq ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"but the cause is eternally right , \"","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"he wrote in his memoir .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Most criticism of Rubio , as of Bush , has focused on his bone-headed performance on a question","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"both men had to be prepared for .","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"And it ' s true ,","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"they both looked like nincompoops .","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"But in fact , the problems for the two are deeper than performance .","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"Neither can say clearly","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"that the war was a mistake ,","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"because they remain close to the neocons in their worldview ,","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"and","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"as I showed Friday ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"the neocons don ' t believe","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"it was a mistake .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Many either knew","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Saddam didn ' t have WMDs","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"or weren ' t mainly invading","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"because of it .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"As a British intelligence official famously said about the Bush administration ' s manipulation of evidence :","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"\" The intelligence and facts were being fixed around the policy . `` .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Fast forward a dozen years ,","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"and Rubio ' s been trying to challenge Bush for neocon support .","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"Check out his campaign tagline","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"-- `` Join Marco 's Fight For A New American Century ! '' -","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"which suggests homage to the Project for a New American Century , peddlers of the Iraq war","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"( Jeb Bush signed their founding document . )","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"Florida ' s junior senator was thought to have less chance","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"to win solid neocon support with George W. Bush ' s brother in the race .","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"But Bush ' s stumbles might have increased his standing .","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"That ' s why he worked so hard","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"not to say","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"it was a mistake ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"even if he looked like an idiot in front of Chris Wallace .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":205,"left":174,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":106,"right":173,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":105,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":105,"left":0,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":117,"right":172,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":117,"left":109,"right":116,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":109,"left":4,"right":108,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":108,"left":5,"right":107,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":107,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":113,"right":115,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":8,"right":112,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":110,"right":111,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":110,"left":9